long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
PetsTab is the Best Cute Animal New Tab Theme For Chrome, Here HD Wallpaper Collection of Dogs, cats, horses, and many more Pets.

Every time you open a new tab, it will provide you with a gorgeous wallpaper at random from its enormous collection of daily wallpapers.

You can apply and decorate your chrome browser, You can easily swap all the theme by visting our site "https://petsthemes.com/" where you have to click Apply wallaper button then boom your new tab theme is change.

It will comes with lots of features like Effects, Todo, Change wallpaper online and many more. If you don't like the layout, Just click the change layout option and you find there is 6 layout in the list.

Feature of PetsTab: Cute Animal New Tab Theme For Chrome:-

1. Unique and HD wallpaper in every new tab.
2. Seperate option to hide/unhide search box and time
3. Change Wallpaper by just visiting site.
4. Change your new tab layout by choose 1 option from the list.
5. All the bookmarks have a seperate section.
6. You can easily set your ToDo list.
7. You can write your notes and Important things.
8. Lots of special effects like snowball, color snowball, rain, fireworks and Autumn levaes.
9. All the Google apps and Social apps are listed.
